  "text": [
    "Sheets entangle him",
    "Naked on his bed",
    "Like a toppled mast",
    "Slack sails bedeck",
    "At sea, no ballast",
    "For that even keel",
    "He cannot keep\u2014",
    "No steering wheel",
    "As he falls asleep"
  ],
  "title": "Heat Wave",
